{"tid":1363293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好撚攰呀]放假係屋企涼冷氣打機唔好？點解要走上街咁辛苦作賤自己？","createTime":"2019-07-25T06:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T09:18:55.000Z","uid":63822,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe8150ad3a157f3a675db9f5be0eb17f4b5dc87","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:33:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為個政府仆街呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求一日未滿足，再辛苦都上街呀<br />\n<br />\n香港人忙就世界聞名，估唔到放假都冇得抖<br />\n<br />\n727雖然係支線任，但大家都要比心機<br />\n<br />\n728主線，去完727既各位唔該，點攰都要全力以赴<br />\n<br />\n仲有明天726既機場同伊利沙伯醫院和理非集合<br />\n<br />\n每日起身同臨訓前入來check一check個任務欄，唔好失焦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/HCity_MissionBoard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHCity_MissionBoard&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=fd576495\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/HCity_MissionBoard</a><br />\n<br />\n大家記住邊個搞到我地30幾度冇冷氣嘆，要行到身水身汗，仲令一班手足受傷<br />\n<br />\n矛頭一致<br />\n<br />\n不撤不散"},{"pid":"a659969487565bb3540e45270640c244b463744c","tid":1363293,"uid":208452,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n《生於亂世，有種責任》<br />\n唔好意思阻阻大家，我地想幫香港人出書，想收集大家意見<br />\n<br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b4d1794f458e9b9f13b4feae1cfaf8af81c6d4c1","tid":1363293,"uid":52364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:36:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"522202bea11516d75028987b461c4e7d16ebaa7f","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"我好撚攰呀，好想放假做自己喜歡既運動，或者同一班朋友出去飲飲食食<br />\n<br />\n係政府同中聯辦令我地呢班後生一至五返完工，六日都冇得抖<br />\n學生哥成個暑假都奉獻哂出來<br />\n<br />\n認住係邊個令我地咁辛苦"},{"pid":"406c74fc531c979f412f1560cf86ebeacc4c0b46","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a2348ab86613e0c17f498eb1068b61270fce0c0f","tid":1363293,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"勾刀"},{"pid":"2107a352ff12db15115e23c84bdba979a2b2f699","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:45:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"349b607256d47748fb3928bc5cc88cb1091d618e","tid":1363293,"uid":207867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"推呀垃圾政府"},{"pid":"dcf2bb378896ea091301fbd161ad47e16ab99998","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:58:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71fef24ed9f702c2998c56125f16d6629e7cb194","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b30faff0c9c03ef38fc9236ddd222f5d1133e545","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:00:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff10ceff6298f20caa54a241e471f77be1e84d0b","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6719a68dc6016958a76733a33aeae4fb5d2f4a8d","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1247d13bb3f00a7c1d212550bb6a8106556d5ee6","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abbcafd1c72cad1f4ed0dcf9dd3b1795e3a25879","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:06:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><code>（瞄準政權）上環黑警36槍企圖殺害抗爭者 中共策劃元朗恐襲</code></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">所有嘢都係中共係背後策劃<br />\n如果呢個政權係仆街係十惡不赦<br />\n咁擁護佢嘅黑警 黑社會都一樣咁仆街<br />\n咁十惡不赦 但唔好浪費咁多時間係呢<br />\n班卒仔到 <br />\n主力打大佬 瞄準返中共 唔好out focus唔係就真係對唔住咁多位被呢個政權殺害嘅戰友</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4LYjFvR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4LYjFvR.jpg&h=d444c005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">義士宣言：不排除成立臨時立法會</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721宣言</span></span>  <br />\n    <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=cfd08e81\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350879\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350879</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">[長文] 時代周刊直指港府失去管治香港能力嘅分析</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356861\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356861</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支持前線所有決定</strong></span></div></span><br />\n民情，輿論，選票，呢啲唔洗我哋去諗，點去收拾所謂嘅殘局，就交比啲政治人物去煩啦<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋要做嘅係我哋認為啱嘅事</span></strong></div><br />\n<code>「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）</code><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">五大訴求，勿忘初衷\n遍地開花，不撤不散\n打倒軍權，反對國家恐怖主義\n光復香港，時代革命</code></pre><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察戰線:</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gq6kYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gq6kYx.jpg&h=1f5648e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hY7P3bT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhY7P3bT.jpg&h=5c1777d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n定性721黑警上環血腥鎮壓，元朗黑社會恐怖襲擊，警黑合作散播中國國家恐怖主義:<br />\n警察冇預警下開槍射36發橡膠彈，有人爆頭，警察已無視通例，已失去合法性<br />\n警察放任黑社會打市民，完全冇制止，並假指無發現武器收隊，傳媒發現雙方實有公開溝通<br />\n警察公然無視電話求助，元朗警署落閘，違反警隊職責<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑社會戰線:</span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7DWJcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7DWJcw.jpg&h=92c6a934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idEKR5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidEKR5S.jpg&h=e6380dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拉攏任何政治冷感市民，有錢人，元朗問題非個別事件，收錢恐襲任何區都會發生，任何人都有機會中招<br />\n俾藍絲睇到佢地支持何君堯即係支持黑社會打人斬人，令藍絲同何君堯反面<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際戰線:</span></div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒巴團隊</span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/RhkvtuUcntXSuoVzay/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FRhkvtuUcntXSuoVzay%2Fgiphy.gif&h=254e8117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLink:<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandwithhk%2F&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=e9a6df03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standwithhk/</a><br />\nTwitter:<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStand_with_HK&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=79ef5bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Stand_with_HK</a><br />\nInstagram:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstandwithhk_%2F&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=5ada6d95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/standwithhk_/</a><br />\nYouTube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=8f6c513a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCyi42Y5o1ksO_yFItyHW7Jw</a>[/quote]<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n[我都要攬炒][時事台]一齊上twitter將黑警濫權揚威國際，警告遊客不要來港旅遊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325723\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325723</a><br />\n攬炒巴登報呢場仗未完!! 大家快D上Twitter!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360410\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360410</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n向外國抗議中國政府散播國家恐怖主義<br />\n向外媒及各國投訴香港警察包庇黑社會合作各自無差別打人，違反通例無預警開槍，已失去合法性<br />\n港鐵作為國際地鐵聯盟之一公然妄顧市民安危強逼市民離開車廂被打<br />\n黑社會涉嫌在元朗發動恐襲襲擊，主腦直指中共政府<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">自發治安戰線:</span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sf52DMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsf52DMn.jpg&h=ecc7650f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[quote][member][size=6][limegreen]"},{"pid":"e579da504cb6e8a0710aabd964bedd6d8631b406","tid":1363293,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"民間自衛隊公海group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkcivilpro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkcivilpro&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=72f65014\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkcivilpro</a>[/limegreen][/size=6][/member][/quote]<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港防衛隊  正式成立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1342844\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1342844</a><br />\n【HKSDF】香港自衛隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352390\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352390</a><br />\n民間保衛隊初形 公民團結行公義 任何抗命運動適用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351343\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351343</a><br />\n【元朗恐襲】真心，如果眾籌，成立「香港自衛隊保安公司」優先過登報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346745\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346745</a><br />\n</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">思想革命戰線:</span></div></span><br />\n平民遊戲工作室出條政治片十分值得思考<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357566\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357566</a><br />\n劉細良 香港內戰<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QbJTdHbdGIU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQbJTdHbdGIU&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=2b7b76bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QbJTdHbdGIU</a><br />\n\t<br />\n梁天琦 本土自治勇武抗爭嘅理由<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/36olyar0wHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F36olyar0wHE&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=cf46112d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/36olyar0wHE</a><br />\n\t<br />\n梁天琦 革命<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVEUhAVki0DA&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=25456a69\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><str